text: "I Don't Think, I Know" is a pop country song written by Brooke McClymont and Clive Young, produced by Charles Fisher for McClymont's second single released in Australia on 2 December 2002 as a CD single. It became McClymont's highest selling solo single to date peaking at number forty-five on the Australian ARIA Singles Chart and spending fourteen weeks in the top one hundred."ARIA Report: Issue 682 - 17th of March 2003". ARIA Charts.
